7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Podcastle and Resemble AI share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Speech, Voice Cloning, Custom Voices. Where Podcastle pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Speech To Text and Noise Removal and Podcast Editing, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Resemble AI uniquely offers Multilingual and Api Access and Real Time, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Podcastle holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Resemble AI scores 7/10 overall and 5/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Resemble AI comes in at a lower starting price of $0.006/sec, while Podcastle begins at $11.99/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Podcastle's free tier and Resemble AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
